  "title": "Junior Brand Ambassadors (Work w friends, fasthire)",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are seeking a reliable and detail-oriented individuals to assist with customer engagement and event execution. Looking for people with a positive attitude and able to work in a fast-paced environment.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Energetic approach towards promoting our services</li>\n  <li>Daily outdoor meeting people from all walks of life</li>\n  <li>Excellent customer service</li>\n  <li>Strong learning attitude and able to adapt in fast pace environment</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with team members to ensure smooth execution</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>PERKS:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Travel regionally with us for events and workshops</li>\n  <li>Lucrative weekly payouts</li>\n  <li>Development sessions</li>\n  <li>Great career support</li>\n  <li>High Pay-Out</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>REQUIREMENTS:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>0 job experience needed</li>\n  <li>Good tech skills</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and closely as a team</li>\n  <li>Ability to handle chinese-speaking customers is a plus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>BE SHORTLISTED WITHIN 2-3 WORKING DAYS!</strong></p>",
